"€19.95, round_nearest_10 converts ¥1,234 → ¥1,230"
msgstr ""
"Exemples : charm_99 convertit $20.50 → $19.99, charm_95 convertit €20.50 → "
"€19.95, round_nearest_10 convertit ¥1,234 → ¥1,230"

